  "description": "Real headlines, but with a point of view. Ugly Press pulls genuine news and hands each story to an AI journalist that adds context, analysis, and commentary instead of just aggregating links. Every day a two-host AI podcast recaps what happened so you can listen on your commute, at the gym, or while making coffee. Skim the feed, dive into a single story, or let the hosts walk you through the day — no endless doomscrolling, no clickbait, just the news with someone actually thinking about it and telling you why it matters.",
